You actually are in #Candidat-followup.Niveau_etude or equivalent. You can apply to a wide range of programs in Marine Engineering, Mechanical Science, IT and Human Science for Engineers:

- Master's degree (MSc - Master of Science): a 2-year program for BSc or equivalent graduates

    Maritime Engineering
    Hydrography
    Automotive Engineering
    Mobile Robotics
    Electronics Systems and Software Design and Security

- Diplôme d’ingénieur : Msc in Engineering
A multi-disciplinary core curriculum, covering the major technological fields (Mathematics, ICT, Mechanics) and Human Sciences. 9 specialized courses.
